      • getArcLayerName

        public static String getArcLayerName(String aPrefix)
        Get the annotation layer name for arc AnnotationType such as AnnotationTypeConstant.DEPENDENCY or AnnotationTypeConstant.COREFERENCE based on the origin span type. This is assumed that an arc is drawn only from single span type such as from POS. For Free Annotation type, the method should be changed.

      • getSpanLayerName

        public static String getSpanLayerName(String aPrefix)
        Get the annotation layer name for span AnnotationType such as AnnotationTypeConstant.NAMEDENTITY or AnnotationTypeConstant.COREFRELTYPE. If this name is changed in the database, the AnnotationTypeConstant constants also should be updated!
